# Search Members

# Description

Search for a guild/server member.

# Project compatibility

Windows | Cross-platform

# Configuration

* 
* Server - Select the server/guild from the available drop-down list. This field supports String type input.
* Username - Enter the username(s) or nickname(s) of the member. This field supports String type input.
* Limit - Maximum records to return in the response. The range is from 1 to 1000. This field supports Int32 type input.









* Search members - Automatically generated output variable.
